idates have not filed with the FEC, and financial data for those candidates are therefore not available.\n\n{{legend|silver|Withdrawn candidate}}\n\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n! rowspan=2 | Candidate\n! data-sort-type=currency rowspan=2 | Total raised\n! colspan=3 | Individual contributions\n! data-sort-type=currency rowspan=2 | Debt\n! data-sort-type=currency rowspan=2 | Spent\n! data-sort-type=currency rowspan=2 | {{abbr|COH|Cash on hand (as of December 31, 2019)}}\n|-\n! data-sort-type=currency | Total\n! data-sort-type=currency | Unitemized\n! data-sort-type=number | Pct\n|-\n|-\n|Armstrong<ref>{{cite web |title=ARMSTRONG, KENNETH REED |url=https://www.fec.gov/data/candidate/P00012104/ |website=Federal Election Commission |access-date=February 23, 2020}}</ref>{{efn|Armstrong's most recent financial report was for the period ending December 31, 2019.}}\n| $20,360\n| $16,608\n| $4,909\n| 29.56%\n| $1,867\n| $17,054\n| $734\n|-\n|Behrman<ref>{{cite web |title=BERHMAN, DAN TAXATION IS THEFT |url=https://www.fec.gov/data/candidate/P00009696/ |website=Federal Election Commission |access-date=February 2, 2020}}</ref>\n| $42,064\n| $7,767\n| $1,500\n| 17.23%\n| $18,660\n| $42,064\n| $0\n|-\n|[[Lincoln Chafee|Chafee]]<ref>{{cite web |title=CHAFEE, LINCOLN DAVENPORT MR. |url=https://www.fec.gov/data/candidate/P60008075/ |website=Federal Election Commission |access-date=March 31, 2020}}</ref>\n| $62,546\n| $2,496\n| $1,996\n| 79.97%\n| $0\n| $50,119\n| $12,427\n|-\n|Dunham<ref>{{cite web |title=DUNHAM, KEENAN WALLACE |url=https://www.fec.gov/data/candidate/P00013284/ |website=Federal Election Commission |access-date=2 February 2020}}</ref>\n| colspan=\"7\"| ''filed statement of candidacy''\n|-\n|Gerhardt<ref name=\"GerhardtFEC\" /><ref>{{cite web |title=GERHARDT, ERIK CHASE |url=https://www.fec.gov/data/candidate/P00012153/ |website=Federal Election Commission |access-date=2 February 2020}}</ref>\n| colspan=\"7\"| ''filed statement of can