{"title_page": "Madhumita Sarkar", "text_new": "{{Use dmy dates|date=July 2019}}\n{{BLP sources|date=June 2015}}\n{{Infobox person\n| name               =         = \nn            = A capture from bojhena shey bojhena\n| birth_date         = 26 October 1994\n| birth_place        = [[Kolkata]], [[West Bengal]], [[India]]\n| residence          = [[Kolkata]], [[West Bengal]]. [[India]]\n| nationality        = [[India]]n\n| other_names        = \n| occupation         = [[Actor]], [[Model (person)|Model]]\n| years_active       = 2011-present\n| known_for          =[[Sobinoy Nibedon]], [[Care Kori Na]], [[Bojhena Se Bojhena (TV series)|Bojhena Se Bojhena]] and [[Kusum Dola]]\n| website            = \n}}\n\n'''Madhumita Sarcar''',  is an Indian [[television]] [[actress]] and model from [[Kolkata]], best known for playing the lead roles of, Pakhi Ghosh Dostidaar Singha Roy''<ref name=\"pakhi\">{{cite news |url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/tv/news/bengali/Why-is-Pakhi-of-Bojhena-Shey-Bojhena-called-Dhopas-Kumari/articleshow/27181320.cms |title=Why is Pakhi of Bojhena Shey Bojhena called Dhopas Kumari? |work=[[The Times of India]]}}</ref> and ''Dr. Emon Mukherjee'' in the television serials respectively. Her recent movie [[Love Aaj Kal Porshu]] released on 14th February 2020 received good appreciation from Critic <ref>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/bengali/movie-reviews/love-aaj-kal-porshu/movie-review/74148170.cms</ref>. She also acted in Bengali web series Judgement Day <ref>https://www.bollywoodlatestforu.com/2020/03/madhumita-sarkar-age.html</ref> <ref>https://www.zee5.com/zee5originals/details/judgement-day/0-6-2162</ref> along with [[Sohini Sarkar]], a ZEE5 originl, is currently streaming.\n\n==Television==\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|- style=\"background:#ff9; text-align:center;\"\n! Year !! Serial !! Character !! Channel\n|-\n| 2011-12 || ''[[Sobinoy Nibedon]]'' || Naina || [[Sananda TV]]\n|-\n| 2012-13 || ''[[Care Kori Na]]'' || Jahnnabi Mukherjee aka Juni || [[Star Jalsha]]\n|-\n| 2013\u201316 ||  ''[[Bojhena Se Bojhena (TV series)|''Bojhena Se Bojhena'']] '' || Pakhi Ghosh Dastidar Singha Roy and Khushi (double role)|| [[Star Jalsha]] \n|-\n| 2016    || ''[[Meghbalika]]'' || Shreyoshi || [[NTV (Bangladesh)|NTV]] Bangladesh\n|-\n|2016\u201318 || ''[[Kusum Dola]]'' || Dr. Emon Chatterjee (n\u00e9e Mukherjee) || [[Star Jalsha]]\n|}\n\n== Filmography ==\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n| style=\"background:#ffc;\"| \n| Denotes films that have not yet been released\n|}\n\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|- style=\"background:#cfc; text-align:center;\"\n| '''Year''' || '''Film''' || '''Role''' || '''Director''' || '''Co-Actor''' || '''Language'''\n|-\n|rowspan=\"2\" | 2020 || ''[[Love Aaj Kal Porshu]]'' ||  || [[Pratim D. Gupta]] || [[Arjun Chakraborty]] || Bengali\n|}\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n\n\n==External links==\n* {{twitter|iamadhu}}\n* {{instagram|madhumita_sarcar}}\n\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Sarkar, Madhumita}}\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Place of birth missing (living people)]]\n[[Category:Indian television actresses]]\n[[Category:Indian soap opera actresses]]\n[[Category:Year of birth missing (living people)]]\n", "text_old": "{{Use dmy dates|date=July 2019}}\n{{BLP sources|date=June 2015}}\n{{Infobox person\n| name               = Madhumita Sarcar (Rhea)\n| image              = \n| caption            = A capture from bojhena shey bojhena\n| birth_date         = 26 October 1994\n| birth_place        = [[Kolkata]], [[West Bengal]], [[India]]\n| residence          = [[Kolkata]], [[West Bengal]]. [[India]]\n| nationality        = [[India]]n\n| other_names        = \n| occupation         = [[Actor]], [[Model (person)|Model]]\n| years_active       = 2011-present\n| known_for          =[[Sobinoy Nibedon]], [[Care Kori Na]], [[Bojhena Se Bojhena (TV series)|Bojhena Se Bojhena]] and [[Kusum Dola]]\n| website            = \n}}\n\n'''Madhumita Sarcar''',  is an Indian [[television]